      "text": "When I visited India in 2019 I did not understand the \"shower\" in the bathroom. There was no shower-head. There was simply a tap on the wall and a large bucket with a jug on the floor. I worked it out that the water had to go in the bucket and then I could pour it over myself with the jug. A great compromise between a shower and a bath! A great way of making people aware of their use of a very scarce resource in that part of India."
