      "text": "Last year Marc and I were \"homeless\" for a while and slept a number of nights on Marc's boat. We used the shower at the harbour: This involved putting coins in a machine - x cents bought 3 minutes of hot water in the shower. Again a great system to make you aware of the \"cost\" of water."
