      "text": "These are forms of rationing. It got me thinking about universal basic income. Again this is a continuous flow concept but of a transmutable resource. Will the money be spent on the foundations of shelter, warmth, water and food or will it be spent gambling or a host of other addictions? Why not give a ration of the things that are needed that can't be so easily transmuted? I am thinking a ration of water, food, electric, space to sleep...."
